urdu transliteration text:
Karnay ko dua Rab say,mein hath uthati houn,ameen kaho bacho,ameen kaho bacho
O children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC

Who pyaas ka aalam hai, lab khola nahi jata,kuch bola nahi jaatamein harfe dua apne ashkon ko banaati hunAmeen kaho bacho
O children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC

Paani jo mein kismat say, thora sa bhi paaungiAsghar ko pilaaungibas ek dua lab par, roro kay mein laati hunAmeen kaho bacho
O children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC

Mei chain na paaungi, ammu se judaa hokar,marjaaungi roro karAllah mein tujhe apni, faryaad sunaati hunAmeen kaho bacho
O children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC

Who uth kay Madinay say, aajaaengi darya par,deti hun sada rokarammu hai musibat mein, dadi ko bulaati hunAmeen kaho bacho
O Children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC

Shabbir kay khayme mein, Nayyar hai bapa matam,aati hai sada Mesumpyaasi hu Sakina hoon, roti hoon rulaati hoonAmeen kaho bacho
O children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC

Darya say abhi apnay, ammu ko bulaati hunAmeen kaho bacho
Please, O children, say Aameen
@HujjatELC
